Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:34.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
