Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the executives of the Donquixote Family \Nhave been taken down one after another,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Doflamingo alone remains.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:58.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he has caused the Birdcage to constrict\Nin order to kill all the people in the country.{\i0}
